3 PAGE worked for Charlie Playforth
3 DATA
4 TEXT Thomas Calvin Anderson, husband of Pauline Playforth Anderson worked for Charlie Playforth.  Charles Floyd Playforth is Pauline Playforth's uncle.  Charles was a cabinet maker during this decade and worked all the way to Michigan but lots of work i
5 CONC n Crab Orchard, Kentucky building a row of houses across from where his parents lived when they moved to town.  Bernard, Charles son, would live in that house from the time he was 13 years old till Bernard's death.  
