2 CONC : auto; line-height: normal;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'times new roman';"&gt;She was born Jan. 22, 1922, in Florida Station, Ind., and lived in this area most of her lif
2 CONC e, before moving to Arizona in 1982.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</line><line>&lt;p style="mso-margin--alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast
