2 CONC n style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'times new roman','serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'times new roman';"&gt;Survivors include her children, Penny King (companion, James Reinhart) of Sun City West, Ariz., Debby (Steve) Lennis of Muncie, Ind.
2 CONC , and Sam Spoo of Overgaard, Ariz.; sister, Faye Starrett; brother, Russell Ashby; eight grandchildren, 10 great-grandchildren; and several nieces and nephews.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</line><line>&lt;p style="mso-margin--alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom
