2 CONC eora (Brown) Ashby; son, Steven Spoo; five sisters; and four brothers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</line><line>&lt;p style="mso-margin--alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto; line-height: normal;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt; font-family: 'tim
