2 TITL Barber Manufacturing History
1 _OID 2abbfb6c-a5c9-4757-840c-5a3891b441e2
1 PLAC Anderson Indiana
1 _DSCR Barber Manufacturing
2 CONT 1824 Brown St • P.O. Box 2454 • Anderson, IN 46016
