1 _OID b65102b8-5921-4573-a1a2-5dcabba2d782
1 _META <metadataxml><content><line>&lt;p&gt;My son had his autosomal DNA done at 23andme. He matches 3 people that have ancestors in Rockcastle Co., KY., one is a lady and her nephew that have Joseph Carson and Mary Evans as ancestors, from their son Davi
2 CONC d Carson that married Catherine Lawrence, my son's ancestor is Ruthy Carson, sister to David, that married Tartulus Lawrence, brother to Catherine. Tartulus and Catherine Lawrence's parents were William and Sarah Lawrence. He also has a match wit
2 CONC h a guy that has James Proctor and Mary Brenneman as ancestors from the son, William Henry Green Proctor, that married Mary Carson Lawrence, daughter of Tartulus and Ruthy Carson Lawrence. My son's ancestor is James Proctor, son of James and Mary P
2 CONC roctor. I will add to this story if he gets more matches on the same chromosones. Janeen Davis Proctor 8/28/13 Update: 10/5/13: two 5th cousin that are from James and Mary Proctor's daughter, Elizabeth Cook, and her daughter, Margaret Fish.&lt;/p&g
2 CONC t;</line></content></metadataxml>
