1 _DSCR ASHBY, Branch obit:   from Anderson Public Library,  Anderson Daily Bulletin dated Saturday, 23 Feb 1957    Branch ASHBY, 74, Florida Station, d. 22 Feb 1957 at St. John's Hospital.  Arrangements were made through the Nuckols & Carmichael Funeral H
2 CONC ome.  Burial was to be in the I.O.O.F. cemetery in Frankton, Indiana 25 Feb 1957.    Mr. ASHBY wa born in Madison Co., son of Mr. & Mrs Ryan ASHBY and he had resided in the Florida Station area most of his life.    Survivors listed were a sister Mr
2 CONC s. Byrtle BRUMMETT of Florida Station with whom he had made his home; 2 brothers Sam and Clyde ASHBY, both of Anderson..    
