1 _META <metadataxml><content><line>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: normal; background-color: #dcd0cf;"&gt;Christian Harness Sr (son of Martin Harnish and Magdalena Martin) was born 1722 in Lancaster Pennsylvania, and died 1770 in Fr
2 CONC edericks Virginia. He married Barbara Hiestand, daughter of Henry Hiestand. Christian was in Augustas County, VA by 1748, where he had witnessed the will of his brother in law, Johannes Hockman husband of Barbara Harnish Hockman (Christian's sister
2 CONC ). Hockman's will was written in German and English. Christian's name was spelled Harness in one place of the document and Harnish in another. After this Christian's name and many of his descendants would appear as Harness.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</
2 CONC line></content></metadataxml>
