2 CONC iv&gt;</line><line>&lt;div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"&gt;BARKER Ruby (nee Playforth), beloved wife of the late Palmer Barker; devoted mother of Trevis Barker, Leah (Don) Friend, Claudia (Randy) Taylor, and Kimberly (DeWayne) Howell; lovin
2 CONC g grandmother of 10 and great grandmother of 8; dear sister of Everett Playforth. Member of Mill Road Church of Christ. July 19, 2006. Age 83 years. Friends may call at the Vorhis Funeral Home, 11365 Springfield Pk., Springdale, Saturday, July 22
2 CONC , 2006 from 9 A.M. til time of service at 11 A.M.&lt;/div&gt;</line><line>&lt;div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;</line><line>&lt;div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; wi
